      "The poem says wisdom cannot be purchased. What are the ways our culture tries to buy or earn wisdom?",
      "What is the difference between knowledge and wisdom in your own experience?",
      "'The fear of the Lord is wisdom' — is this a satisfying answer or a deflection?",
